| Item | Cost |
|------|------|
| NFC Rings (100) | $400 |
| App development | Team time (3-4 months) |
| L2 deployment | ~$100 |
| Hosting/infra | ~$50/month |
| Testing/iteration | Ongoing |
| **Total** | **~$1,000 + dev time** |

